      "module_path": "ref_verify",
      "docs": "Secondary adapter implementing `RefVerifierPort` by dispatching to the Chain-specific capability (`ref-verifier-chain1` for Chain1, `ref-verifier-chain2` for Chain2) resolved from the `cache_scope` argument passed to `verify_pair` (D11, CN-11, CN-12). Handles fast/final round resolution via `AgentProfiles.resolve_execution`, renders the capability-specific prompt template (`prompt_template_path`), and delegates execution to an injected `AgentExecutionRunner` callable with `(ResolvedExecution, rendered_prompt)` (D7, CN-01, AC-01, AC-12, AC-15). No timeout: D13-1/CN-13 removed timeout_seconds. The concrete `Arc<AgentExecutionRunner>` implementation is provided by the infrastructure layer (see `make_ref_verifier_process_runner`); cli-composition wires the DI only and must not contain subprocess-spawn / process-management / OS-specific syscall logic.",
      "spec_refs": [
