      "module_path": "ref_verify",
      "docs": "Infrastructure adapter that resolves IN-12 caller context into the RefVerifyScope passed to the usecase. Scope is context-sensitive rather than file-presence-only: SpecDesign resolves to Chain1, TypeDesign { layer } resolves to Chain2 { layer }, and CommitGate/Standalone resolve to All. The adapter still reads spec.json and TDDD catalogue files to validate required artifacts and layer ids, but phase/mode selection comes from the typed RefVerifyInvocationContext supplied by cli-composition. cli-composition wires this at the DI root and translates call sites into the context enum; the usecase layer receives the resolved RefVerifyScope via RefVerifyCommand and does not perform I/O itself. track state I/O is infrastructure's responsibility (D9, IN-12).",
      "spec_refs": [
        {
          "file": "track/items/sot-chain-semantic-review-gate-2026-06-07/spec.json",
          "anchor": "IN-12",
          "hash": "852c06b9f7e3ec94b581daf6e96ceb1dd2c69339b1b8314504b8b049d6d14d9a"
        }
